project: Move fruits using your mouse or touch.
Click on the playing field to drop the fruit.
When two fruits of the same type are touched, they can be combined into a larger fruit at the next level.
If the fruit overflows from the box, then game over.

They are 11 types of fruits in total. Follow the image below to evolve from left to right.

Try to evolve the fruit into a watermelon so that you can put more fruits in the box.
